    <item>
      <title>中东和非洲视野 07/31/2024</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-31/horizons-middle-east-africa-07-31-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈马斯称，高级领导人伊斯梅尔·哈尼耶在参加新伊朗总统就职典礼后，在以色列对德黑兰发动的空袭中丧生。此前，以色列称，为报复周六戈兰高地的袭击，以色列在贝鲁特发动的空袭中杀死了一名真主党高级指挥官。节目中还报道了：日本央行上调了基准利率，并公布了将债券购买量减半的计划；汇丰银行的诺埃尔·奎因在其首席执行官任期的最后一个季度中，又向股东返还了 30 亿美元。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-31/horizons-middle-east-africa-07-31-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 06:46:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒梅尔称法国将推进预算进程</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/france-will-push-ahead-with-its-budget-process-le-maire-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[布鲁诺·勒梅尔表示，法国看守政府正在采取必要措施，确保议会能在秋季对预算法案进行表决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/france-will-push-ahead-with-its-budget-process-le-maire-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 06:25:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特经济因 OPEC+ 减产连续第四个季度萎缩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/saudi-economy-gdp-contracts-for-fourth-quarter-on-opec-oil-curbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于 OPEC+ 减产继续给这个全球最大石油出口国的经济带来压力，沙特阿拉伯的国内生产总值连续第四个季度小幅萎缩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/saudi-economy-gdp-contracts-for-fourth-quarter-on-opec-oil-curbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 06:19:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿迪达斯在美国的批发业务增长更快且改善</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/adidas-shows-faster-wholesale-growth-and-improvement-in-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿迪达斯公司 (Adidas AG) 报告称，其批发收入出现反弹，北美地区（不包括 Yeezy 运动鞋的销售额）恢复增长，该品牌在经历多年危机后希望提高利润。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/adidas-shows-faster-wholesale-growth-and-improvement-in-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 06:00:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾金融管理委员会称外国投资者股票销售仅限于“短期”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/taiwan-s-fsc-says-foreign-investor-stock-sales-only-short-term</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾最高金融监管机构表示，近期海外投资者抛售股票属于“短期现象”，并不代表看跌观点，近年来外资持股一直呈上升趋势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/taiwan-s-fsc-says-foreign-investor-stock-sales-only-short-term</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 05:59:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲需求强劲，达能销售额超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/danone-sales-beat-forecasts-amid-strong-asia-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[达能公司 (Danone SA) 表示，随着生活成本压力的缓解和部分亚洲市场的复苏，消费者开始重新购买更昂贵的品牌商品。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/danone-sales-beat-forecasts-amid-strong-asia-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 05:35:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>微软报告 Azure 云增长放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-31/microsoft-reports-slower-azure-cloud-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[微软股价在盘后交易中收复了大部分失地。该公司报告称，其 Azure 云部门增长放缓。这一结果加剧了投资者的担忧，他们急切地希望看到人工智能带来的回报。彭博社的 Ed Ludlow 对此进行了更多报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-31/microsoft-reports-slower-azure-cloud-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 05:28:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
